            "detailed_description": "Balance of Kingdoms is about building, balancing and battling, combining elements of strategy and physics. Players must build a kingdom balanced on top of a beam while trying to defeat their opponent.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Build</h2>Build your Kingdom with limited resources and prepare for battle or test yourself with a series of Build Challenges.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Balance</h2>Be careful where you place your buildings! Your Kingdom is on top of a beam which will need to be kept balance! In a battle you can use this to your advantage and attempt to unbalance your opponent's town!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Battle</h2>Test your building and balancing skills against an opponent. Just watch out for their cannon fire!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Singleplayer</h2>See how long your Kingdom can last in the Survival mode or build without any time or gold limits in Freebuild mode. <br>After early access each Kingdom will have their own singleplayer campaign and story.",
            "about_the_game": "Balance of Kingdoms is about building, balancing and battling, combining elements of strategy and physics. Players must build a kingdom balanced on top of a beam while trying to defeat their opponent.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Build</h2>Build your Kingdom with limited resources and prepare for battle or test yourself with a series of Build Challenges.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Balance</h2>Be careful where you place your buildings! Your Kingdom is on top of a beam which will need to be kept balance! In a battle you can use this to your advantage and attempt to unbalance your opponent's town!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Battle</h2>Test your building and balancing skills against an opponent. Just watch out for their cannon fire!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Singleplayer</h2>See how long your Kingdom can last in the Survival mode or build without any time or gold limits in Freebuild mode. <br>After early access each Kingdom will have their own singleplayer campaign and story.",
